snippet.textDisplay: Everytime I think her voice can't get anymore beautiful...it does🥰 I think she's one of the most beautiful young women out there...after my daughter, of course♥️ I cried from the start of her crying cause I've watched Demi grow up since Barney. This song is the life we all know so well. We all feel lost, broken, like no one could ever feel the pain and loneliness we feel at that moment in time. The sad part is if we all just brought one another up instead of ripping them down there wouldn't be so much pain😞 Try to remember the kid at school next to you that is on top of the world may cry themselves to sleep at night, cause they are lonely. The kid that seems out of place could be dealing with abuse. We never know what someone else is going through. All the $$ in the world can't buy love♥️ Today hug someone who needs it. Say something nice to someone you think may not hear it often. Always know we all need somebody♥️
